    {
      "id": "1b14750c-f3ba-80a8-a891-f9ffc73381be",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "DKT has an issue with interpretability, despite its well-document success at modelling student knowledge. Authors draw from Multi-Dimensional Item-Response Theory and Cognitive Learning to create XKT, an explainable Knowledge Tracing Model. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1b14750c-f3ba-80a8-a891-f9ffc73381be",
        "parent": {
